VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT \b(?:window\.open|cordova\.InAppBrowser\.open)\s*\(
WHEN EXPR MISSING:allowlist|trustedUrls|validateUrl|startsWith.*https && MISSING:test|example
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects browser launch calls that require URL validation and allowlist checks.
TRACE Externalized mobile rule logic for Insecure External URL Handling.
